I agree with Logo. Lets get a bit creative. Like "Son of a maintenance bot" 
or "piece of scrap" or other TF related things. Bitch, fuck, and the other 
human words like that don't fit into a robot war.

::Zardus::

Zardus frowns as he watches Battera fly away, activating his comm.

"Battera," he says into it, looking back at Rage, "Where are you going?"
